  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A study to establish the efficacy of a new type of mechanical rotational chair in treating
      BPPV. In addition, comparison of three types of treatment maneuvers using the mechanical
      rotational chair.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Open-label, randomized controlled trial comparing three different treatment maneuvers in a
      mechanical rotational chair (ROTUNDUM-chair) in treating BPPV. Patients diagnosed with BPPV
      will be randomized to one of three maneuvers in the ROTUNDUM-chair:

        1. Epley's maneuver

        2. Semont maneuver

        3. 360 degree vertical rotation
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
